The paper discusses distributed data stream processing and edge computing, which are topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and networking (cs.NI). It also covers resource elasticity, which is a concept related to database systems (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses challenges and solutions for achieving elasticity in distributed systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
